    <font color="#FF0000"><i>[Quote from original post: Is there any way so that
    when we log on to the server screen, we can see what servers we have
    characters on?]</i><br>
    </font><br>
    No, as each account logging in would have to query all of the world servers.
    I imagine that at some future point we might be able to put something in
    client-side, but it would be very low priority. I imagine that people
    generally dont need help remembering where their characters are.<br>
    <br>
    <font color="#FF0000"><i>[Quote from original post: Do we just need to log
