    Why am I seeing so many posts along these lines? We do have ways of
    determining what is in game and in what numbers. Truthfully, if it were only
    a matter of a couple on each server, we would have written them off as lucky
    and left them in game as is. But that isnt the case. There are quite a few
    of them on each server, though each poster here might only be aware of a
    few. There are roughly 8000 accounts playing on each server, half of which
    have characters capable of acquiring those items where they existed. No one
    person can say with certainty how many there are without direct access to
    our database.<br>
